[[Image:Moscow, Khlebny Lane 28, Embassy of Iceland.jpg|thumb|right|Embassy of Iceland in Moscow]] The '''Embassy of the Republic of Iceland in Moscow''' is the [[diplomatic mission]] of [[Iceland]] in the [[Russian Federation]]. It is located at 28 [[Khlebny Lane]] ({{lang-ru|Хлебный переулок, 28}}) in the [[Presnensky District]] of Moscow.<ref>{{cite web |title=About the Embassy |publisher=[[Ministry of Foreign Affairs (Iceland)]] |url=http://www.iceland.org/ru/english/ |accessdate=2008-06-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080510152940/http://www.iceland.org/ru/english/ |archivedate=2008-05-10 |df= }}</ref>
