{{notability|1=Events|date=July 2018}}
[[File:Formulaz.jpg|thumb|right|200px|Handmade Wooden Car Race - Red Bull Formulaz, Turkey 2017]] '''Formulaz''' is an annual [[Laz people|Laz]] festival and traditional wooden [[Auto racing|car race]] held each year on the 21st August, in the northern [[Turkey|Turkish]] province of [[Rize Province|Rize]]'s [[Ardeşen|Ardeşen district]].<ref>[http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/rizes-fourth-formulaz-races-wooden-made-cars-28349 Hurriyetdailynews.com] Rize’s fourth Formulaz races wooden made cars</ref><ref>[https://www.dailysabah.com/turkey/2015/08/10/formulaz-wooden-car-race-a-treat-for-slow-drivers Dailysabah.com] Formulaz: Wooden car race a treat for slow drivers</ref> The name itself comes from the contraction of the word '[[Formula One|Formula]]' with '[[Laz people|Laz]]', which is the name used for the local people living on the edge of the [[Black Sea]] in Northern [[Turkey]].<ref>[https://www.redbull.com/int-en/formulaz-race-pov-video Redbull.com] ''Try this brakeless wooden car – it’s awesome''</ref>
==See also== *[[Kolkhoba]]
