{{Unreferenced|date=December 2012}} {{Infobox Union |name= NUEYS |country= [[Eritrea]] |affiliation= |members= |full_name= National Union of Eritrean Youth and Students |native_name= |image= [[File:NUEYS logo bright small-size.jpg|150px]] |founded= 1978 |current= |head= |office= Keskese St. 173 No. 27, [[Asmara]], [[Eritrea]] |people= |website= [http://www.nueys.org Official website] }}
The '''National Union of Eritrean Youth and Students''' (NUEYS) is dedicated to improving the skills and awareness of Eritrean youth. The organization seeks to strengthen and improve the youth in all aspects on the regional, national and international levels.
NUEYS has branches throughout [[Eritrea]] as well as the world to serve the Diaspora.
